{
  "title": "Palaciat maduq",
  "titleCh": "小米起源說",
  "soundPath": null,
  "sentence": [
    {
      "chinese": "傳說古時有兩個太陽，大地十分貧瘠，無法滋長食物，人類苦苦哀求天神恩賜糧食。天神答應恩賜人類糧食，並啟示要撒下種子。有一天，耆老看見一隻「dangqachuqhuq（前胸紅色的鳥）」，飛到住屋上方撒下不知名的種子。過了許多年，仍然看不到大地上有長出什麼東西來。",
      "ab": "Matu iha’anang qabasdaingaz maiza dau dusa’ ca vali tudiip, mantaan dau maqahqah sala ca kaidalaqan dii, niit samu na taldai’as kakau’nun, makanmiqdi’ ca bunun masusumsum makuscaiv is kakau’nun. Ua’ antala’us Diqanin ca sinluluklac, ua’ macaiv bunun is kakau’nun, mapasnava’ tu na maqasqas is quqsa. Maiza dau tatdiqanin, saduu dau ca madaingaz is dangqachuqhuq tu luqai’, makadaza’ dau lumaq maqasqas is niit kalulun a quqsa. Laqai’in piapia ta’ qamisan a, qaltu nii’ang lungu saduu ti maiza ma’az ca minhauluk ha’an dalaqi’.",
      "order": "1",
