    {
      "chinese": "長者囑咐孩子們說：來一起鬆土吧！是否會找到天神所賜的食糧，究竟是在哪裡？從一根被斬斷的樹根，滴下了汁液，未見過的小苗就從那裡滋長起來。族人小心地呵護這陌生的植物，直到長出了一串穗子。",
      "ab": "Maskalun ca madaingaz is uvava’az tu, muskuna qan makakais dalaqi’! Mucqa’ang naupa inku’anas sincaiv is Diqanin a kakaunun, na ica qa naupa qa? Minaca’an dau latasqatan a lamis is lukici’ tutuduc ca tiquc, minaca’an ta’ dau ca nii’ang samu sinaduu’an a camang minciqaung.",
