    {
      "chinese": "穗子成熟後，由長者將一粒穗子放進嘴裡嚐嚐，瞬間充滿了飽足感。族人便深信這是天神所賜的食糧，因為一粒米就能夠讓一家人吃飽。這就是天神所恩賜且有靈的食物，族人稱之為「maduq（小米）」。",
      "ab": "Macacakin dau ca laac, ciat tatini ka madaingaz ca siza’ ta’a tuza’ a laac pukumbu’ is ngulus tanam ma’un, matinsuu’ dau tan’as ki’abuqan. Minlatuza’ ca Bununi’ tu icia Diqanin sincaiv tu kakaunun ca dii, maupa’i maca ta’a tuza’ a laac is tilac dii ha, maqtu’ pi’abuqan is maitatlumaq tu bunun. Tutuza’ ac kini’ tu sinkadaidaz is Diqanin sincaiv ca dangi’as Is’ang a kakaunun dii, ua’ patingaanas Bunun tu maduq.",
